# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NEVER commit virtual machine images or appliances — they are multiple GB
# and do not belong in git. The repo tracks documentation and evidence only.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.vdi
*.vmdk
*.vhd
*.vhdx
*.ova
*.ovf
*.vbox
*.vbox-prev
*.iso
*.img
*.img.gz

# VirtualBox default VM directory, if it ever lands inside the repo
VirtualBox VMs/

# Large or raw capture files — keep sanitized excerpts as text/PNG instead
*.pcap
*.pcapng

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# NOTE: evidence/*.png screenshots ARE tracked on purpose — they are small
# and are the proof the design works. Do not ignore them.
